name: Louisa Quainoo
description: I am some one who tries to live fully each day.Not waste any time focused on the negatives and what ifs, accept people for who they are and where they are at. Relish the times with friends and family. I have a compassionate heart for “most” people. Probably a little too trusting and gullible at first. I love to challenge myself with knew knowledge and yet go deeper with God everyday in time for prayer and meditation. I love to sing , it makes me feel carefree and childlike, a great way to express myself. I love and care deeply and have found in being that way that forgiveness is the key to truely loving others and mostly forgiving myself.
